Anatomy of a Woebot® (WB001): agent guided CBT for women with postpartum depression
Alison Darcy, Aaron Beaudette, Emil Chiauzzi, Jade Daniels, Kim Goodwin, Timothy Y. Mariano, Paul Wicks & Athena Robinson
