reported medium or high degrees of therapeutic alliance and acceptability (WAI-SR ≥ 24). WB001+TAU participants had significantly larger improvements in PHQ-9 depression scores as compared to a TAU-only control group (p = .025) between delivery and 6 weeks postpartum. Baseline mean (standard
